{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Scavenge the Battlefield:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore ancient battlefields to gather resources, tools, weapons, and armor. Pack your backpack strategically using a Tetris-style minigame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/Desc_Battlefield.png?t=1739463435\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rebuild and Expand the Bastion:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct and upgrade buildings, from warehouses and workshops to towering fortifications and training grounds. Build vertically on the massive Bastion wall for maximum efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/Desc_Build.png?t=1739463435\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft and Prepare:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn scavenged resources into valuable equipment. Assemble gear sets to arm your defenders for the battles ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/Desc_Craft.png?t=1739463435\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defend Against the Undead:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for relentless undead sieges by strategically positioning your defenders and optimizing your Bastion for survival in tactical siege simulations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/Desc_Siege.png?t=1739463435\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deep Progression System:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock over 400 progression nodes to gain powerful weapons, new buildings, and player upgrades.</p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/Desc_Achievements.png?t=1739463435\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/i